      <title>民調顯示，這次對歐盟選舉的興趣更高</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/interest-eu-election-higher-this-time-around-poll-shows-2024-04-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[週三公佈的一項歐盟民調顯示，歐洲人對即將舉行的歐洲議會選舉的興趣明顯高於五年前上次投票前，貧窮、健康、就業和國防被視為首要競選議題。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/interest-eu-election-higher-this-time-around-poll-shows-2024-04-17/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 05:04:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
